{"tid":1560391,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(915) 12點英領、3點銅鑼灣","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:32:50.000Z","uid":254330,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4ce1b92979c49b265d1c47e8e51a0164948d66","tid":1560391,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaofeU2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaofeU2.jpg&h=6afa883c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLPNQug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLPNQug.jpg&h=151013ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UVGMmBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUVGMmBn.jpg&h=1742e5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><em>915 915 915 915 915</em></ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">15 September </span><br />\n12點,英國領事館🇬🇧<br />\n12pm,British Consulate🇬🇧 (Nearby Admiralty Station)<br />\n3點,銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n3pm,East Point Road (Nearby Causeway Bay Station)<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再講英國幫唔到手所以去黎冇用,英國作為《中英聯合聲明》嘅其中一個簽署國,佢係可以介入嘅。英國唔敢介入?你班仆街唔撚去make noise,冇番咁上下人數,點敢介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?你唔出黎都好意思話人唔介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?Freedom is not free!<br />\n英國有政治力量,美國有軍事力量,政府咁怕我地搵外國勢力,<span style=\"color: red;\">證明靠外國勢力可以揸實佢另外果粒春袋</span>!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> God save the Queen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> God save Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直落3點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要再次逼爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要嗌英文口號,唔好淨係得中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比外國知道,香港人仲未放棄,唔會接受政府嘅條件,堅持<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求,缺一不可</span>!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FIVE Demands<br />\n<br />\nNO ONE LESS!</span></span><br />\nFight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\nNo Rioters, Only Tyrannies!<br />\nHong Kong Police is Murderers!<br />\nNo <del> China </del>, Free Hong Kong!<br />\nDemocracy Now! Human Rights Now!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our times!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FIVE Demands<br />\nNO ONE LESS!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">915 港島見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e522c35d77a1ef17febe72d61721f86efabefe1f","tid":1560391,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請即參與：#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1</a><br />\n已有手足推緊hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n向外國人宣傳警暴！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=81b2e2db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n或者share以下既圖去twitter<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n3. 叫埋外國人一齊Report俾WhatsApp聽，增加noise<br />\n尾數雙數先係business，單數係正常account<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係兩種acc都違反晒terms of service！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n班狗想分散投資，不過我地要port到佢一條不留！<br />\n<br />\n祝大家舉報愉快<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxr6aC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxr6aC.jpg&h=ab2b926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqeBKbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqeBKbL.jpg&h=93c8393e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a93477de41f1c8b564beb0ed9b06690c0000c91e","tid":1560391,"uid":20283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"915呀 又冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"beb49683d2536e6c384f591ec73c938fa9c37a3f","tid":1560391,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3912afec5a95e2400918e464b00efeab548d860b","tid":1560391,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"FIVE Demands, NO ONE LESS!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f39a8317cd2952ecbaa6f275d9e81f05a3d64e2","tid":1560391,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aab103b3b6590a7305c91f1ee515ddc950e8cbe7","tid":1560391,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"Say NO to #ChiNazi"},{"pid":"264113d521e427ea9d294fec996b97461c71545d","tid":1560391,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d125d9ed2b68934e0ab41db0f383fb2f311bfd32","tid":1560391,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5dbc8eefdbb15e0bcf5251039f807caf8f71b9","tid":1560391,"uid":289179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"去呀屌 未贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src